items.description: AI-Powered Sales Intelligence System untuk perusahaan X yang menganalisis 5,663 pelanggan menggunakan Machine Learning untuk memberikan rekomendasi strategis penjualan melalui framework Next Best Offer (NBO).

items.name: XAI
items.description: Explainable AI (XAI) framework designed to provide transparent, interpretable insights for both tabular and image-based machine learning models.

items.name: miglan
items.description: Framework for Data Science and Machine Learning

items.name: portfolio
items.description: I'm a Results-driven Software Engineer with expertise in computer vision and machine learning applications. My journey in tech has been fueled by a passion for creating intelligent systems that solve real-world problems.  With a strong background in Python programming, deep learning frameworks, and image processing technologies.

items.name: passive-dns-ml-evaluation
items.description: Passive DNS threat detection using lexical machine learning techniques. This repository contains a reproducible research prototype and experimental evaluation framework for assessing the feasibility, accuracy, and performance of machine-learning-based malicious domain detection in a passive DNS monitoring context.

items.name: FedEasy
items.description: FedEasy is an intuitive powerful yet simple to use Federated Learning framework. Our goal is to streamline the process of setting up and running federated learning experiments with ease, making advanced machine learning techniques accessible to researchers and developers alike.

items.name: stock-forecast
items.description: A repository focused on implementing machine learning frameworks and statistical methods to predict the closing price of a stock

items.name: Factor-Mining-Framework
items.description: This project implements a complete quantitative research pipeline for mining, combining, and evaluating alpha factors. It covers the entire lifecycle from data simulation and feature engineering to machine learning optimization (Elastic Net) and rigorous performance testing (Quantile Backtesting, IC Analysis, and Factor Decay).

items.name: machinelearning
items.description: ML.NET is an open source and cross-platform machine learning framework for .NET.

items.name: hyrax
items.description: Hyrax - A framework for machine learning in astronomy

items.name: sagemaker-distribution
items.description: A set of Docker images that include popular frameworks for machine learning, data science and visualization.

items.name: fairness_ontology
items.description: A comprehensive and extensible ontology for systematically modeling fairness notions, metrics, biases, evaluation methods, and scientific provenance in machine learning. This ontology provides researchers, developers, and practitioners with a unified, machine-readable framework to guide the design and assessment of fair ML systems.

items.name: tensorflow-federated
items.description: An open-source framework for machine learning and other computations on decentralized data.

items.name: ML-Framework-for-Depression-Risk-Stratification
items.description: A Machine Learning Framework for Depression Risk Stratification Among University Students: Integrating Predictive Performance with Dual Interpretability Techniques

items.name: XAI-for-Solar-Electrolysis-Green-Hydrogen-Production-and-Yield-Optimization
items.description: Reproducible framework for forecasting and optimizing green hydrogen production from solar-powered electrolysis using physics-informed feature engineering, interpretable machine learning (SHAP/LIME), and scenario analysis. Includes public data pipeline, Python notebooks, figures, and LaTeX tables for full transparency.
